<p>Friday afternoon is a great time for many people, end of the week with the weekend in sight.</p>

<p>However, when Snapchat experiences an outage, the entire world seems to crumble.</p>

<p>Thousands flocked to DownDector, which monitors issues that may arise with online platforms and services, to share the problems they are experiencing using the app. </p>

<p>The majority of complaints were aimed at sending snaps, but others are also unable to receive them.</p>
